I make things that solve problems.

Can you tell us a little bit about your experience and the work you do?
I do digital consultancy for small and medium businesses, everything from websites to content strategy.

How has Postmark helped you?
Postmark helped me build a free service to help people with Multiple Sclerosis (MS) find the most relevant research and clinical trials.

How are you using Postmark on your projects today?
We send a weekly digest of relevant MS research to patients and doctors. And also, we also notify them by email of new or updated clinical trials.

What advice would you give other folks in your role about implementing and managing their email?
You can be the best at what you do, but nobody can do everything alone. For
